  <FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.5.node.nodes.1.text>The raiders have already engaged the settlers you were asked to protect!</FCP_Quest_SettlementRaidDefense.root.nodes.14.node.nodes.5.node.nodes.1.text>
